);\\\">Power Steering</span></li></ol><h6><strong style=\\\"background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.87);\\\">Seals &amp; Gaskets on Covered Parts Only</strong></h6><h6><strong style=\\\"background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.87);\\\">Features</strong></h6><ol><li data-list=\\\"bullet\\\"><span class=\\\"ql-ui\\\" contenteditable=\\\"false\\\"></span><strong style=\\\"background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.87);\\\">Select “No Limits Per Claim” </strong><span style=\\\"background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.87);\\\">With a liability cap of $20,000, our Gold Plans offer exceptional coverage.</span></li><li data-list=\\\"bullet\\\"><span class=\\\"ql-ui\\\" contenteditable=\\\"false\\\"></span><strong style=\\\"background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.87);\\\">Quick &amp; Stress-Free Claims Process:</strong><span style=\\\"background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.87);\\\">Get Covered Canada is committed to a fast and seamless claims process, allowing you to select your preferred repair shop.</span></li></ol><h6><strong style=\\\"background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.87);\\\">Coverage for Vehicles Less than 7 Years Old</strong></h6><ol><li data-list=\\\"bullet\\\"><span class=\\\"ql-ui\\\" contenteditable=\\\"false\\\"></span><span style=\\\"background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.87);\\\">We provide tailored plans for new or used vehicles of any age. Speak with one of our Customer Service Associates to find the right coverage for your vehicle.</span></li></ol>\"', '[{\"productName\":\"60 Months/105000 KM\",\"productPrice\":\"1439\"},{\"productName\":\"48 Months/105000 KM\",\"productPrice\":\"1249\"},{\"productName\":\"36 Months/85000 KM\",\"productPrice\":\"1029\"},{\"productName\":\"24 Months/65000 KM\",\"productPrice\":\"799\"},{\"productName\":\"12 Months/50000 KM\",\"productPrice\":\"609\"}]', './I